    "rationale": "All 13 V&V 40 credibility factors assessed. Twelve factors meet or exceed required levels. One factor (Test conditions) achieves level 2 against a required level of 3 due to single-temperature testing; this shortfall is acknowledged and accepted given that ASTM F1717 is a standardized room-temperature protocol and the device is not intended for elevated-temperature environments. Overall credibility is sufficient to support a Medium assurance level decision for this Class II device.",
